com.anthem.selenium.constants

Interface DateTimeConstants

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DateTimeUtils

    public interface DateTimeConstants
    This interface declares the Date and Time Formats.
    Date Constants starting with _ returns the format with - separator.
    Date Constants not starting with _ returns the format with / separator.
    Time Constants starting with _ returns the 24hr format with : separator.
    TIme Constants not starting with _ returns the 12hr format with : separator.
    eg:- DateTimeConstants.Date_Format_5
    Author:
    shiva.katula
